title: Can the Lakers or Bucks Amass 73 Wins? | The Mismatch
description:
With the Lakers and Bucks on a crash course to meet each other with identical 25-3 records, we wonder whether each team can continue its torrid pace (11:30). Also, Luka’s twisted ankle (2:25) and trades that could change the league (28:49).

Hosts: Chris Vernon and Kevin O’Connor
